Preview a bulk-enrichment cost given a set of job titles applied to the current selection. Returns `{selected_leads, enriched_contacts, enrichable_contacts, title_suggestions, auto_included_titles, previously_enriched_titles}`. `previously_enriched_titles` is a newer field (in prod soon) — when present, the agent can recommend repeating those titles for new leads.

{{include:headers/tool-when-to-use}} between selecting leads and launching, to know what the enrichment will cost.

{{include:headers/tool-when-not-to-use}} from agent flow — leadbay_enrich_titles wraps preview + launch with the right safety checks.
